data.description: RUSTIC COUNTRY CHARM! If you're looking to escape the hustle and bustle, this beauty fits the bill with its 2.39 acres of pristine land included!! The main house includes 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths and from the moment you step in from the welcoming front porch through one of the sets of French doors, you'll notice the attention to detail throughout. A great open living area features the expansive living room and kitchen with convenient bar seating, rich, custom wood cabinetry and a walk-in pantry to thrill any chef! Gorgeous hand-made burnt wood barn doors grace all the openings along with trim and accent walls to bring it all together. The spacious comfortable master en suite includes a private bath and walk-in closet. The additional guest bedrooms on the other wing of the split plan are huge and would accommodate a large family nicely along with another full bath. Through the back doors you'll find another relaxing porch that overlooks the pool/outdoor kitchen area and enjoy watching the wildlife that roams freely. The fully detached apartment makes a wonderful guest/in-law suite and boasts a huge living space, 2 bedrooms, full bath and kitchenette, great for all your family gatherings! The fully fenced property also includes a huge workshop/garage with 220v electric service and plenty of loft storage as well. Enjoy exploring your own private paradise including a pond stocked with various types of fish and and a chicken condo with your very own flock. There's also a hookup to keep your RV charged and ready to go. The rock-finish split face block provides strength and ease of maintenance and the reinforced truss strapping gives peace of mind during any storm. Furnishings as shown with the exception of artwork and personal items convey with the sale making this one truly "move-in ready".  Schedule your appointment to take a look at this gorgeous home today!!
